long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Make your favorites more private.

* Save website to favorites.
* Easy manager favorites, delete favorites and drag to sort favorites.
* Open all favorites by one click.
* Open favorites in an incognito window.
* All favorites are only saved on your machine, and will not be uploaded to the remote server.
